364
00:28:37,452 --> 00:28:39,018
Sim, Khanoum.

365
00:29:01,610 --> 00:29:03,076
Isaac.

366
00:29:04,980 --> 00:29:07,413
Barton.

367
00:29:07,415 --> 00:29:09,349
Vartan Sofoyan.

368
00:29:10,185 --> 00:29:11,885
Meu Deus.

369
00:29:13,188 --> 00:29:14,821
Ha três semanas atrás,

370
00:29:14,823 --> 00:29:16,756
você estava ensinando
Shirin a tocar violino.

371
00:29:16,758 --> 00:29:18,491
